Let me take a look at you.

116
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,460
He didn't hurt you, did he?

117
00:06:24,750 --> 00:06:25,880
I'm fine.

118
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:26,720
I'm fine.

119
00:06:27,750 --> 00:06:28,560
General.

120
00:06:28,870 --> 00:06:30,190
-You must…
-Yimeng.

121
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:34,090
