122
00:06:36,560 --> 00:06:37,360
Well...

123
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,270
Well...

124
00:06:38,909 --> 00:06:39,830
Hong.

125
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,510
Hong.

126
