You've finally been released.

129
00:06:49,390 --> 00:06:50,560
So don't go against him

130
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:51,650
in court anymore,

131
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:52,320
okay?

132
00:06:52,340 --> 00:06:53,020
Yimeng,

133
00:06:53,560 --> 00:06:54,600
be honest with me.

134
00:06:55,040 --> 00:06:56,840
He bullied you today, didn't he?

135
00:06:57,390 --> 00:06:58,190
Sure enough.

136
00:06:58,630 --> 00:07:02,000
Second male leads are always
the ones the audience falls for.

137
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,390
They're just better.

138
00:07:11,190 --> 00:07:11,950
Isn't this…

139
00:07:11,950 --> 00:07:13,330
This piece of jade was gifted to me

140
00:07:13,330 --> 00:07:14,600
by my aunt,

141
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:16,310
the late empress, when I was born.

142
00:07:16,310 --> 00:07:17,600
It's protected me on the battlefield,

143
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,730
bringing me home safe again and again.

144
00:07:20,020 --> 00:07:21,720
Now that we're getting married,

145
00:07:21,720 --> 00:07:22,850
I want you to have it.

146
00:07:23,130 --> 00:07:24,330
May it protect the one

147
00:07:24,570 --> 00:07:26,010
I love from today on.

148
00:07:27,080 --> 00:07:28,360
Even Nan Heng

149
00:07:28,390 --> 00:07:29,560
wouldn't dare act recklessly

150
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:31,490
in front of something from my aunt.

151
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,310
But

152
00:07:33,310 --> 00:07:34,600
if you give it to me,

153
00:07:35,010 --> 00:07:35,960
what about you?

154
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:46,040
I have the scented pouch you gave me.

155
00:07:48,340 --> 00:07:50,940
During those dark days
in the imperial prison,

156
00:07:51,270 --> 00:07:53,470
it was the only thing that kept me going.

157
00:07:56,050 --> 00:07:57,790
But this jade is so valuable.

158
00:07:58,159 --> 00:07:59,190
My scented pouch

159
