169
00:08:22,980 --> 00:08:23,780
So beautiful.

170
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:31,000
Every time our general sees Miss Song,

171
00:08:31,210 --> 00:08:32,020
he acts like

172
00:08:32,549 --> 00:08:34,480
a peacock spreading his feathers.

173
