Miss Song.

174
00:08:39,919 --> 00:08:41,450
Greetings, Your Highness.

175
00:08:42,549 --> 00:08:44,150
You and Guihong
have been engaged since childhood.

176
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,390
Strictly speaking, marriage

177
00:08:45,390 --> 00:08:46,550
is a bond between two families.

178
00:08:46,550 --> 00:08:48,210
It's meant to last till death.

179
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:50,170
But now Guihong's career

180
00:08:50,170 --> 00:08:51,290
is in jeopardy,

181
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,750
and the rumors about you and Heng
are spreading like wildfire.

182
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:54,670
So tell me,

183
00:08:54,670 --> 00:08:56,140
is the engagement still valid or not?

184
00:08:56,140 --> 00:08:57,190
Your Highness,

185
00:08:57,350 --> 00:08:59,010
that's between Yimeng and me.

186
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,080
I'm your cousin.

187
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:03,670
You're still an outsider.

188
00:09:03,670 --> 00:09:04,480
Guihong.

189
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,700
Your Highness.

190
00:09:05,890 --> 00:09:07,320
In this world,

191
00:09:07,440 --> 00:09:09,720
the last person I'd ever get involved with

192
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:10,670
is Nan Heng.

193
