We can't even be friends,

194
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,550
let alone lovers.

195
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:19,200
Because no one knows better than I do

196
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:20,600
that he's actually

197
00:09:20,600 --> 00:09:22,440
a monster in disguise.

198
00:09:23,650 --> 00:09:25,060
So please rest assured.

199
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:26,250
As long as

200
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,270
Hong

201
