205
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,390
Great!

206
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:37,550
Oh, you flatter me.

207
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:38,690
I'm just speaking from the heart.

208
00:09:38,690 --> 00:09:40,150
If you like hearing it,

209
00:09:40,170 --> 00:09:41,770
I can say even more.

210
00:09:41,870 --> 00:09:42,870
Sure.

211
00:09:43,250 --> 00:09:44,460
No need, Yimeng.

212
00:09:44,510 --> 00:09:45,320
It's getting late.

213
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,250
Let's head back.

214
00:09:46,260 --> 00:09:48,590
Th-then see you next time, Your Highness.

215
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:49,600
Leaving already?

216
00:09:54,920 --> 00:09:56,180
What a perfect couple.

217
00:09:57,630 --> 00:09:58,710
Lovely.

