227
00:10:22,670 --> 00:10:24,900
Why did that bloodthirsty maniac
have to ruin everything?

228
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:25,910
I'm telling you,

229
00:10:25,910 --> 00:10:27,120
my days

230
00:10:27,270 --> 00:10:28,750
