241
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,440
You've never

242
00:10:50,440 --> 00:10:52,440
suffered like this your whole life.

243
00:10:59,440 --> 00:11:00,500
Don't be dramatic.

244
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:02,840
It hurts.

