has already been wiped out by me.

289
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,940
You really think this pathetic force

290
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,630
can fight against my Xuanjia Army?

291
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:33,270
You overestimate yourself.

292
00:13:34,740 --> 00:13:36,300
Traitor Nan Heng!

293
00:13:37,030 --> 00:13:39,000
You murdered your own father for power

294
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,660
and slaughtered your own kin.

295
00:13:41,060 --> 00:13:42,390
Your claim to the throne

296
00:13:43,090 --> 00:13:44,640
is illegitimate

297
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:45,950
and unjust!

298
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:47,750
Today,

299
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,890
I'll seek justice for the people

300
00:13:51,040 --> 00:13:52,450
and take you down!

301
00:13:53,070 --> 00:13:54,260
Take me down?

302
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:01,550
You've brought troops into the palace.

303
00:14:01,550 --> 00:14:02,910
To the people,

304
00:14:03,190 --> 00:14:04,670
you're nothing but a rebel

305
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:05,840
and a joke.

306
00:14:06,580 --> 00:14:07,780
Killing you

307
00:14:08,360 --> 00:14:09,760
is perfectly justified.

308
00:14:13,350 --> 00:14:14,480
Chu Guihong.

309
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:18,120
Your woman is now part of my harem.

310
00:14:18,740 --> 00:14:20,830
Your brother is dead by my hand.

311
00:14:21,460 --> 00:14:22,860
And now,

312
00:14:23,550 --> 00:14:25,000
I'm taking your life too.

313
00:14:30,930 --> 00:14:32,530
If you want someone to blame…

314
00:14:34,050 --> 00:14:35,120
blame yourself

315
00:14:35,690 --> 00:14:37,220
for choosing the wrong side

316
00:14:37,520 --> 00:14:39,010
from the start.

317
00:14:39,050 --> 00:14:39,660
[Guangde Gate]

318
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,750
Miss, it's time for your wellness routine,

319
00:14:43,750 --> 00:14:44,860
just as you instructed.

320
00:14:44,860 --> 00:14:46,510
You scared me half to death.

321
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:49,670
Xia,

322
00:14:49,780 --> 00:14:51,780
you're really good to me.

323
00:14:52,390 --> 00:14:53,200
But…

324
00:14:53,730 --> 00:14:55,190
isn't this tonic

325
00:14:55,330 --> 00:14:56,850
a little too strong?

326
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,070
Not at all.

327
00:14:58,200 --> 00:15:00,150
The Lantern Festival
is just around the corner.

328
00:15:00,150 --> 00:15:02,550
The elders say
eating ginseng during the festival

329
00:15:02,550 --> 00:15:04,630
will bring good fortune
for the whole year.

330
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,830
What did you just say?

331
00:15:06,300 --> 00:15:07,360
Lantern Festival?

332
00:15:09,130 --> 00:15:10,970
[Iconic scenes in the script]

333
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:14,110
[2: Saving the Girl
at the Lantern Festival]

334
00:15:32,680 --> 00:15:36,760
[Yao Qian, the investigating censor]

335
00:15:38,910 --> 00:15:41,720
The evening breeze
stirs the candle's glow.

336
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:45,560
His Highness leans over his desk,
not resting on a pillow.

337
00:15:50,870 --> 00:15:52,350
At midnight,

338
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:54,660
not a rooster crows, not a dog barks.

339
00:15:54,840 --> 00:15:57,350
Your Highness, why have you suddenly

340
00:15:57,370 --> 00:15:58,320
summoned me?

341
00:15:58,350 --> 00:15:59,200
Get in here.

342
00:16:05,600 --> 00:16:07,780
I placed you in the Censorate

343
00:16:08,030 --> 00:16:10,430
so you'd keep an eye
on things in the palace.

344
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:14,790
You should know…

345
00:16:16,190 --> 00:16:17,920
I have no use for incompetents.

346
00:16:20,540 --> 00:16:21,590
I'm sorry.

347
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,400
I'm terribly sorry.

348
00:16:23,430 --> 00:16:25,270
Please, Your Highness,
give me one more chance.

349
00:16:25,270 --> 00:16:27,440
I'll dedicate myself fully,

350
00:16:27,460 --> 00:16:28,360
just like Your Highness—

351
00:16:28,360 --> 00:16:29,120
working day and night

352
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:30,150
without stopping to rest.

353
00:16:30,150 --> 00:16:31,670
I swear I'll collect

354
00:16:31,670 --> 00:16:32,670
every last piece of proof

355
00:16:32,670 --> 00:16:33,670
of Chu's crimes.

356
00:16:37,030 --> 00:16:37,840
Good.

357
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:40,520
I'll give you a chance.

358
00:16:41,570 --> 00:16:43,670
Then you know what to do

359
00:16:44,370 --> 00:16:46,370
at tomorrow's morning court, don't you?

360
00:16:46,370 --> 00:16:47,500
Yes, Your Highness.

361
00:16:57,360 --> 00:16:59,740
His Majesty has arrived!

362
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:07,040
Long live Your Majesty!

363
00:17:07,790 --> 00:17:08,790
Rise.

364
00:17:09,349 --> 00:17:11,130
Thank you, Your Majesty.

365
00:17:18,920 --> 00:17:19,720
Father.

366
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:20,960
Rui,

367
00:17:21,510 --> 00:17:23,310
do you have something to report?

368
00:17:23,480 --> 00:17:24,270
Father,

369
00:17:24,720 --> 00:17:25,589
I believe that

370
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,880
although the Qianyu Army
suffered a setback this time,

371
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:30,110
Chu Guihong
has earned great merit over the years.

372
00:17:30,110 --> 00:17:31,480
He's a rare military talent.

373
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:33,070
How can we brush him off
with an empty title?

374
00:17:33,070 --> 00:17:33,790
Therefore,

375
00:17:34,000 --> 00:17:35,600
I respectfully request that

376
00:17:35,640 --> 00:17:37,830
you appoint Chu Guihong
to an important post

377
00:17:37,830 --> 00:17:39,550
and return command
of the Qianyu Army to him

378
00:17:39,550 --> 00:17:41,410
so he may defeat Heyuan once more.

379
00:17:41,680 --> 00:17:43,810
Regaining command of the Qianyu Army?

380
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:45,350
Who else but General Chu

381
00:17:45,380 --> 00:17:47,590
is qualified to take on
such responsibility?

382
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:49,840
But didn't he just lose a battle?

383
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,260
Exactly.

384
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,940
How can we promote a defeated general?

385
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:57,110
Miss.

386
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:58,920
How did it go?

387
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,510
I handed the pouch you gave me

388
00:18:00,510 --> 00:18:02,790
to that attendant next to General Chu,

389
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,880
Rong Hua,

390
00:18:03,880 --> 00:18:05,030
the big guy

391
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:05,880
who's quite strong,

392
00:18:05,880 --> 00:18:07,670
but his face kinda resembles…

393
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,110
No one asked about Rong Hua.

394
00:18:09,110 --> 00:18:10,160
He's not the point.

395
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:11,240
I'm asking about Chu Guihong.

396
00:18:11,240 --> 00:18:12,130
Did he read it?

397
00:18:12,160 --> 00:18:12,920
He did.

398
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:13,920
And as it happens,

399
00:18:13,920 --> 00:18:14,830
right after

400
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:16,310
he read your message,

401
00:18:16,310 --> 00:18:17,790
someone from the palace showed up

402
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:19,790
and summoned him to see His Majesty.

403
00:18:20,090 --> 00:18:21,400
Miss, what did you write

404
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,790
in your message?

405
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,070
General Chu's expression

406
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:26,070
was really strange after he read it.

407
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:30,190
He read it. That's all that matters.

408
00:18:30,190 --> 00:18:32,830
Good thing I remembered
that part of the plot.

409
00:18:33,080 --> 00:18:34,720
Otherwise...

410
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,810
Heng,

411
00:18:38,840 --> 00:18:40,270
what do you mean?

412
00:18:40,510 --> 00:18:41,400
Every position I proposed,

413
00:18:41,400 --> 00:18:42,960
you shot it down with some excuse.

414
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:44,240
You couldn't kill my cousin,

415
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:46,700
and now you can't even
hide your intentions?

416
00:18:49,490 --> 00:18:50,480
Heng,

417
00:18:50,920 --> 00:18:52,680
since you think the posts Rui suggested

418
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,130
aren't suitable,

419
00:18:54,270 --> 00:18:55,350
then tell me—

420
00:18:55,920 --> 00:18:57,030
what post do you think

421
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:58,480
Chu Guihong deserves?

422
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,790
Your Majesty,

423
00:19:02,440 --> 00:19:03,310
in my opinion,

424
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:05,110
when discussing matters of court,

425
00:19:05,110 --> 00:19:06,910
the public good must come first.

426
00:19:07,310 --> 00:19:09,470
If we give Chu Guihong a high position,

427
00:19:10,310 --> 00:19:12,770
we'll be putting personal interests first.

428
00:19:15,610 --> 00:19:17,940
If appointing the right person for the job

429
00:19:18,000 --> 00:19:20,070
is putting personal interests first,

430
00:19:20,070 --> 00:19:21,920
are you saying

431
00:19:21,920 --> 00:19:24,030
only when the court
is full of the Gao family's people

432
00:19:22,190 --> 00:19:23,630
[Calm, Respectful, and Sincere]

433
00:19:27,310 --> 00:19:29,640
can we say we've put
the public good first?

434
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:34,360
You must be joking, Your Majesty.

435
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:35,400
The Duke of Zhou welcomed talent

436
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,830
and won hearts across the land.

437
00:19:36,830 --> 00:19:38,160
Helping you unite the nation

438
00:19:38,160 --> 00:19:40,070
and recruit men of virtue and talent

439
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:41,070
is what we've

440
00:19:41,090 --> 00:19:42,610
always striven to do.

441
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,240
Your Majesty.

442
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:46,240
Chu Guihong may

443
00:19:46,270 --> 00:19:48,400
have had a good reputation in the past,

444
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:51,000
but after the Pingrong Battle,

445
00:19:51,440 --> 00:19:54,700
his command led to
the loss of tens of thousands of soldiers

446
00:19:55,030 --> 00:19:56,790
and the slaughter of civilians

447
00:19:56,830 --> 00:19:58,160
in three border cities.

448
00:19:58,270 --> 00:19:59,070
As a result,

449
00:19:59,400 --> 00:20:01,530
his reputation is already tarnished.

450
00:20:01,750 --> 00:20:03,350
I worry that reinstating him

451
00:20:03,790 --> 00:20:05,480
will only dishearten the people.

452
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,280
Your Majesty.

453
00:20:08,200 --> 00:20:09,850
[Calm, Respectful, and Sincere]

454
00:20:09,070 --> 00:20:10,480
Greetings, Your Majesty.

455
00:20:10,480 --> 00:20:11,310
Rise.

456
00:20:11,410 --> 00:20:12,810
Thank you, Your Majesty.

457
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,350
Seventh Prince,

458
00:20:17,440 --> 00:20:18,900
you said my reputation is tarnished now.

459
00:20:18,900 --> 00:20:20,680
What evidence are you basing that on?

460
00:20:20,680 --> 00:20:22,140
Naturally, it's backed by

461
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,760
a Censorate investigation.

462
00:20:25,070 --> 00:20:25,880
Your Majesty,

463
00:20:26,750 --> 00:20:28,000
I request that

464
00:20:28,020 --> 00:20:29,540
the investigating censor

465
00:20:29,570 --> 00:20:32,590
present the Censorate's impeachment
memorial against Chu Guihong

466
00:20:32,590 --> 00:20:33,990
and explain the details.

467
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,240
Seriously?

468
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,970
You came prepared, didn't you?

469
00:20:38,480 --> 00:20:39,270
Summon him.

470
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:44,120
[Memorial]

471
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:26,170
Seventh Prince,

472
00:21:26,900 --> 00:21:28,840
may I ask how much longer

473
00:21:28,880 --> 00:21:31,050
until the impeachment memorial arrives?

474
00:21:31,050 --> 00:21:32,190
Yeah, Heng,

475
00:21:32,430 --> 00:21:34,800
it's almost noon now.

476
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:37,720
Don't tell me you sent someone

477
00:21:37,720 --> 00:21:39,300
to write it on the spot.

478
00:21:40,550 --> 00:21:41,410
Your Highness,

479
00:21:42,040 --> 00:21:44,300
there's something fishy about all this.

480
00:21:44,500 --> 00:21:45,260
Maybe…

481
00:21:45,360 --> 00:21:46,560
Wait a little longer.

482
00:21:54,030 --> 00:21:55,020
Guess

483
00:21:55,960 --> 00:21:57,550
I'm really hungry.

484
00:21:58,310 --> 00:21:59,110
Well,

485
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:01,080
putting the right people
in charge matters,

486
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:02,280
but not more than

487
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,400
Father's health.

488
00:22:03,750 --> 00:22:05,160
If we wait any longer,

489
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:06,590
we could skip lunch

490
00:22:06,720 --> 00:22:08,440
and have dinner directly.

491
00:22:08,460 --> 00:22:09,220
Enough.

492
00:22:09,880 --> 00:22:11,610
Since no one has any objections

493
00:22:11,750 --> 00:22:13,600
to reinstating Chu Guihong,

494
00:22:14,110 --> 00:22:16,530
he shall be appointed
as the Prefect of the Capital

495
00:22:16,530 --> 00:22:17,800
and Commander of the Army,

496
00:22:17,800 --> 00:22:19,100
resuming leadership of the Qianyu Army

497
00:22:19,100 --> 00:22:20,210
to guard the capital.

498
00:22:20,210 --> 00:22:21,100
In an emergency,

499
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:22,430
he can act with full discretion.

500
00:22:22,430 --> 00:22:23,700
He can also enter the palace armed

501
00:22:23,700 --> 00:22:25,100
to report directly to me.

502
00:22:32,280 --> 00:22:33,830
Congratulations, General Chu.

503
00:22:33,830 --> 00:22:34,660
No,

504
00:22:35,040 --> 00:22:36,730
now we should be calling you

505
00:22:36,920 --> 00:22:38,160
Commander Chu

506
00:22:38,160 --> 00:22:39,350
or Prefect of the Capital.

507
00:22:39,350 --> 00:22:40,480
It's a great responsibility.

508
00:22:40,480 --> 00:22:41,340
I'll do my best.

509
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,260
I hope all of you

510
00:22:42,270 --> 00:22:43,000
can guide and support me…

511
00:22:43,000 --> 00:22:43,270
Your Highness.

512
00:22:43,270 --> 00:22:44,110
In the days to come.

513
00:22:44,110 --> 00:22:45,310
Just now, Mr. Yao was blindfolded,

514
00:22:45,310 --> 00:22:46,030
beaten,

515
00:22:46,030 --> 00:22:48,240
and left in an abandoned mine
on the western outskirts.

516
00:22:48,240 --> 00:22:49,350
By the time we got there,

517
00:22:49,350 --> 00:22:51,550
the place had already been cleaned out.

518
00:22:59,460 --> 00:23:00,790
No need to investigate.

519
00:23:01,120 --> 00:23:03,180
It must've been Chu Guihong's doing.

520
00:23:04,270 --> 00:23:05,870
But what I can't figure out is

521
00:23:06,550 --> 00:23:08,840
how he knew where Yao Qian was.

522
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:10,050
Your Highness.

523
00:23:10,110 --> 00:23:10,920
Last night,

524
00:23:11,000 --> 00:23:13,160
we sent someone to tail Miss Song.

525
00:23:13,180 --> 00:23:14,950
She ran into Chu Guihong on the road.

526
00:23:14,950 --> 00:23:15,870
And this morning,

527
00:23:15,870 --> 00:23:16,680
a maid from her house

528
00:23:16,680 --> 00:23:18,550
secretly paid a visit to the Chu family.

529
00:23:18,550 --> 00:23:20,090
Do you think they might…

530
00:23:32,250 --> 00:23:33,060
Mr. Song.

531
00:23:33,680 --> 00:23:34,480
Come, come.

532
00:23:34,510 --> 00:23:35,590
Have a seat.

533
00:23:42,110 --> 00:23:44,930
I remember when you visited us as a child,

534
00:23:45,110 --> 00:23:46,270
your favorite treat

535
00:23:46,430 --> 00:23:48,090
was always the crystal cake.

536
00:23:48,310 --> 00:23:49,310
Go on, have a bite.

537
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,680
Yes.

538
00:23:54,810 --> 00:23:56,610
Yimeng loves crystal cakes too.

539
00:23:56,910 --> 00:23:58,040
When we were little,

540
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,570
she used to steal mine all the time.

541
00:24:06,970 --> 00:24:08,260
That's a rude thing to say.

542
00:24:08,260 --> 00:24:09,860
Please forgive me, Mr. Song.

543
00:24:10,350 --> 00:24:11,160
It's fine.

544
00:24:11,550 --> 00:24:14,230
Your father and I
have been close for years.

545
00:24:14,260 --> 00:24:16,510
You and Yimeng have been engaged
since you were young.

546
00:24:16,510 --> 00:24:17,790
In my eyes,

547
00:24:18,180 --> 00:24:20,610
you're already family.

548
00:24:20,880 --> 00:24:22,480
No need to stand on ceremony.

549
00:24:26,000 --> 00:24:27,000
That blade of yours…

550
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:27,790
My Lord.

551
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,310
It hasn't been sharpened.

552
00:24:29,310 --> 00:24:31,240
Yeah, I'll take care of that today.

553
00:24:33,760 --> 00:24:35,010
[Song Residence]

554
00:24:39,110 --> 00:24:39,970
Your Highness,

555
00:24:40,510 --> 00:24:41,840
Chu Guihong's here too.

556
00:24:47,010 --> 00:24:54,210
[Room of Elegance]

557
00:24:55,200 --> 00:24:56,030
Miss,

558
00:24:56,030 --> 00:24:57,720
aren't you the most afraid
of the Seventh Prince?

559
00:24:57,720 --> 00:24:59,030
He's literally barging in right now,

560
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:01,090
and you're not the least bit nervous?

561
00:25:01,480 --> 00:25:03,880
When I sent word
to Chu Guihong this morning,

562
00:25:03,880 --> 00:25:05,790
I already knew Nan Heng would come.

563
00:25:05,790 --> 00:25:07,030
Relax.

564
00:25:07,030 --> 00:25:08,590
He can't kill me now.

565
00:25:08,610 --> 00:25:09,970
I'm not afraid of him.

566
00:25:16,320 --> 00:25:17,770
Your Highness.

567
00:25:26,790 --> 00:25:28,980
How could they serve such cheap tea

568
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:31,670
to the distinguished Seventh Prince?

569
00:25:31,770 --> 00:25:32,680
Yingqiu,

570
00:25:32,710 --> 00:25:34,600
go bring my premium ginseng tea.

571
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:35,070
Yes.

572
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:35,790
Zhixia,

573
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:36,790
where are the pastries?

574
00:25:36,790 --> 00:25:38,480
Four sweet ones, four savory ones—
don't miss a single one.

