00:38:57,320 --> 00:38:58,480
You're just being unreasonable.

864
00:38:58,480 --> 00:38:59,150
One day.

865
00:38:59,660 --> 00:39:00,490
Two days.

866
00:39:00,630 --> 00:39:01,510
Just two days.

867
00:39:03,710 --> 00:39:04,840
But, Your Highness,

868
00:39:05,610 --> 00:39:07,480
I have a small favor to ask.

869
00:39:07,630 --> 00:39:09,190
When you leave later,

870
00:39:09,520 --> 00:39:10,850
can you go out that way?

871
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:12,560
That way.

872
00:39:21,000 --> 00:39:21,710
Your Highness,

873
00:39:21,710 --> 00:39:23,150
aren't we here to deal with Song Yimeng?

874
00:39:22,480 --> 00:39:26,260
[Song Residence]

875
00:39:23,150 --> 00:39:24,930
If we leave like this,
won't it just boost her ego?

876
00:39:24,930 --> 00:39:27,060
She even made you
climb out the window.

877
00:39:27,710 --> 00:39:28,480
Your Highness.

878
00:39:28,480 --> 00:39:29,070
You...

879
00:39:29,090 --> 00:39:29,900
You...

880
00:39:39,770 --> 00:39:41,740
Chu Guihong was invited here by Song Yude?

881
00:39:41,740 --> 00:39:42,750
Yes.

882
00:39:42,950 --> 00:39:44,750
They had a long talk in the study.

883
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:46,920
Looks like the Song family

884
00:39:47,290 --> 00:39:49,950
is getting involved
in the fight for the throne.

885
00:39:50,280 --> 00:39:52,500
If we don't kill Song Yimeng,

886
00:39:52,980 --> 00:39:54,590
she'll become a threat down the line.

887
00:39:54,590 --> 00:39:55,560
Your Highness,

888
00:39:55,580 --> 00:39:57,020
Song Yimeng is cunning,

889
00:39:57,050 --> 00:39:58,550
and now she's got the upper hand on you.

890
00:39:58,550 --> 00:39:59,190
That's...

891
00:39:59,860 --> 00:40:01,390
I may not be able to kill her,

892
00:40:02,000 --> 00:40:02,940
but that doesn't mean

893
00:40:02,940 --> 00:40:04,570
I'm at the end of my rope.

894
00:40:06,160 --> 00:40:08,030
Send word to Waning River Crescent.

895
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:10,450
It's time they proved their worth.
